data.description: *NEAR QUANTICO! REGULAR SALE -END UNIT town home with three finished levels (Over 2000 sqft) and a walkout FULLY FINISHED basement backing to trees and a fenced lot! Features:  Hardwoods, NEWER windows, NEWER Hot Water Tank, nice appliances & kitchen cabinets!  Roof replaced in 2016, New furnace, hot water tank & AC 2015, dual heat pump & air handler 2016, ADT hardwired security system & wireless wif-fi enabled thermostats!   Deck off of the dining room & Gas fireplace!!  Each owner's bedroom has its own full bath and cathedral ceiling!  Fenced rear with THREE SHEDS. WON'T LAST LONG!  Note, the price has been reduced for the new buyer to replace the carpet and paint!  Still an excellent value!!!
